extends layout.pug

block meta
    meta(name="description" content="")
    meta(name="keywords" content="")

block styles 
    link(rel="stylesheet" href="/css/pricing.css")

block main
    h1 Pricing
    form.row#pricing(method="POST")
        .col-lg-4
            .card 
                .card-header 
                    h2 Free
                .card-body
                    p With a Free account, you'll have complete access to:
                    ul.list-group.list-group-flush
                        li.list-group-item Public reports
                        li.list-group-item Public reports
                        li.list-group-item Public reports
                .card-footer
                    input(type="submit" name="plan" value="Get Free Access")
        .col-lg-4 
            .card 
                .card-header 
                    h2 Professional
                    p
                        span.price $99
                        | /month
                .card-body
                    p The Professional plan extends the Free plan's access to our services through the following:
                    ul.list-group.list-group-flush
                        li.list-group-item Public reports
                        li.list-group-item Public reports
                        li.list-group-item Public reports
                .card-footer
                    input(type="submit" name="plan" value="Get Professional Access")
        .col-lg-4
            .card 
                .card-header 
                    h2 Premium
                    p
                        span.price $499
                        | /month
                .card-body
                    p The Premium plan gives you acces to most valuable features of Visbanking's services and capabilities, such as:
                    ul.list-group.list-group-flush
                        li.list-group-item Public reports
                        li.list-group-item Public reports
                        li.list-group-item Public reports
                .card-footer
                    input(type="submit" name="plan" value="Get Premium Access")
        .col-lg-12
            .card 
                .card-header 
                    h2 Enterprise
                    p.price Contact Us
                .card-body
                    p The Enterprise plan allows you full, unlimited access to all of Visbanking's features, including:
                    ul.list-group.list-group-flush
                        li.list-group-item Public reports
                        li.list-group-item Public reports
                        li.list-group-item Public reports
                .card-footer
                    input(type="submit" name="plan" value="Get Enterprise Access")
    section.container-fluid#features 
        h2 Features
        p The idea for this section is to have a table comparing the free, professional and premium plans showing which each plan has and which it doesn't. The table would have a fixed footer prompting for the enterprise plan.
        table 
            thead 
                td Feature/Plan
                td Free
                td Professional
                td Premium
            tr 
                td Feature Name
                td 
                    i.bi-x-lg
                td 
                    i.bi-check-lg
                td 
                    i.bi-check-lg

block scripts 
    script(src="/js/pricing.js") 